search_results.title: Darrin McMahon
search_results.snippet: Darrin M. McMahon (born 1965) is an American historian, author, public speaker, and currently a professor of history at Dartmouth College

search_results.snippet: Darrin M. McMahon is currently the David W. Little Class of 1944 Professor of History at Dartmouth, where he previously held the Mary Brinsmead Wheelock Chair.
